text: Mayskoye () is a rural locality (a village) in Verkhnetroitsky Selsoviet, Tuymazinsky District, Bashkortostan, Russia. The population was 48 as of 2010. There are 4 streets. == Geography == It is located 27 km from Tuymazy, 3 km from Verkhnetroitskoye. == References == Category:Rural localities in Tuymazinsky District
title: Mayskoye, Tuymazinsky District, Republic of Bashkortostan
